Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在富士岡資格賽裏突破萬難獲得第三名的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管生「阿斯拉達」隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝著在北海道舉行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本錦標賽進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中他們遇到了一起綁架案件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人搶奪了一輛高智能方程式逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人在神秘賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布埋德的指示下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒著「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被破壞的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到嫌疑獨犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且救出了被綁架的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第六話  北海道的自然兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要有身為一個賽車手的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.51,0:03:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以隨便吃人家東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦 波比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會好好管教它的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我給它吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 這個很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比它平常一見到陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會亂吼亂叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 今天居然會這麼聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫波比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們正在慢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它突然跑到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是貪吃的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是足球選手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是高智能方程式的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫風見隼人 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你就是風見隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也是個賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然很香啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這些牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從我家牧場裏所出產的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家經營牧場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年高智能方程式大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本冠軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時守實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是全日本的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他在那裏做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正在用手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確定路面狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣能知道路面的狀況？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這麼早就起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天去慢跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人已經自己去慢跑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想慢吞吞的偷懶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子是無法獲勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個小子 竟敢批評我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波比 走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人好像開始有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽車手的自覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.05,0:06:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔的教誨 已經有收穫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼豐盛的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 聽說你為了比賽正卯足了勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁大家都在睡覺的時候他自己已經去慢跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我是賽車手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是芹菜榴樦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喝下去吧 你不是缺乏維他命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的有身為賽車手的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把它喝下去吧,對你有幫助的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就勸過她,要她不用做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是可以喝的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一經明日香的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是可以喝的東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 不是喝下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個北海道賽車場的特微就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼跑道佔了一半左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要一口氣跑完賽車跑道還有魔鬼跑道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要事先決定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以哪一種跑道為主攻的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以隼人能夠完全操控
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」為前提下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 我們來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入圍車隊 車手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有賽車的資料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是去年全日本錦標賽的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在全日本排名第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克利尼賽車隊的時守實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全日本錦標賽第二名的福克斯隊的李園慎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是富士岡錦標賽冠軍隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵車隊的新條直輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著這一位是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早上才剛剛見過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是北海道規模最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴托朗隊的專屬車手大友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十七歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他的名字叫大友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有一個很響亮的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做北方有大友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年全日本錦標賽裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜是只得第五名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他沒有獲得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加世界錦標賽的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來大友他也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼厲害的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人的場地練習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午接著演練輪胎的更換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是魔鬼跑道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要大意 親自去體驗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」 你認為我現在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛技術如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微進步了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微進步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會更進步呢 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脫離彎道的時候 為了防止輪胎打滑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須將車速排高一檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且稍微的轉動方向盤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎車也不能完全地踩死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後再選擇適當的車道行駛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實轉彎跑道的跑法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼的簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大友先生的車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人好像在追趕什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度一直在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友 你是大友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是隼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友 聽說你也是一位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害的賽車手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 你聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人家都稱你為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離地心引力的魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種高低不平的道路 我可是第一次經驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很佩服你的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟練了不就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車速失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對大友說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比賽裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有超越他人這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會笨到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己的弱點告訴別人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子會要了你的命的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…大友他不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把「阿斯拉達」先洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備做輪胎更換練習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次得小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發什麼脾氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔根本就不瞭解大友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以說他的壞話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9秒35
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再練習一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9秒71
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9秒l2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9秒55
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,l0秒42
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設法把更換輪胎的時間縮短
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是維修人員的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次小小的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能決定勝敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道不瞭解它的重要性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介他的專長是在電腦方面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對他太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我當然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.87,0:14:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他光是搜集各種資料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經夠累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是像我們這種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數比較少的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人除了自己的專長之外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得費點心力學習其他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入圍隊伍的平均時間是7秒03
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們如果不設法縮短時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名次就會落後了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續練習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊伍還有我的弱點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使大友不洩漏出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果被其他隊伍知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定會想盡辦法來對付我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是全日本錦標賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上大家早點休息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,養足了精神迎接明天的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 你一直都沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 讓你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對於我們隊伍的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想盡可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去彌補一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是關於在轉彎跑道上 我不能順利地通過地事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為了這件事情才睡不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決的方法其實很簡單的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要一直不斷的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到會為止就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練習 可是現在太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果車田叔他要罵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會替你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每件事情都要做到自己滿意為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要練習到會為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多幾次也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」剛剛從這兒經過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備包圍它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面有三輛車追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道除了我之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的選手也在練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候還在練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子情況好像不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面也有車了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要被推下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 大友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 他們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的好像是要對付「阿斯拉達」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢吞吞地在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開不快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要透過車子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感受各種不同的路面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我做不到 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車速太快 必須要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要接近彎道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊40R
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑道的外側是沼澤地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來擺脫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續前進,隼人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法 大友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太會開轉彎道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是那樣的急轉彎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要相信你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不能相信自己地話 那這場比賽就會輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 我一定辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 換檔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向盤向外轉,拉手剎車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升檔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大友 我通過這個彎道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能是企業間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在世界各地都如火如茶地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從事高智能方程式的開發
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們真的是針對「阿斯拉達」而來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼「阿斯拉達」一定事部非常優秀的車子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不希望借用車子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以自己的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來展現快速的跑法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 越接近比賽的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越希望能夠一個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一個人靜靜地反省
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的實力到底有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己問自己是不是有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠的力量來面對比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一次都得到同樣的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要盡可能做到自己能力範圍里面該做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是誠實的面對自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你剛才也做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的比賽裏面我們就是比賽對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會讓你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.61,0:22:55.87,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有現在加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能有明天的輝煌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:05.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 不用後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:11.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著自己樹立的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:16.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎著風前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:21.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終我們會是勝利者

